- Halo?
- Halo!

419
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:10,235
Brachiosaurus! Besar sekali.

420
00:37:12,404 --> 00:37:17,159
Dooly adalah ceratosaurus.

421
00:37:17,242 --> 00:37:18,702
Lihat ini.

422
00:37:18,786 --> 00:37:20,412
